### Lode Scape 2d RPG
Lode Scape is a 2d role playing game that began development in February of 2013. Most of the progress can be followed [here](http://www.java-gaming.org/topics/wip-2d-rpg-with-no-name/28679/120/view.html) If you have any questions contact me at wreed58@gmail.com
